OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and dull day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain throughout. Rain
OL,7,Fwill often be heavy and persistent but
OL,8,Fsome drier spells possible in the
OL,9,Fsouth over Ayrshire later in the day.
OL,10,FBreezy at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy night with rain
OL,13,Ffeeding in from the west, becoming
OL,14,Fheavy and persistent at times,
OL,15,Fespecially for parts of Argyll. Best
OL,16,Fof any drier spells in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
