OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAnother cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain throughout the day
OL,7,Ffor many. The best of any drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter spells will be in the south
OL,9,Facross Ayrshire. Windy across Argyll.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,FTuesday with further rain spreading
OL,13,Feastwards. Drier on Wednesday with
OL,14,Fsome bright or sunny spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping, especially in the south.
OL,16,FCloudy again on Thursday with some
OL,17,Flight rain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
